  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "托卡列夫 TT-33 7.62x25 手枪",
      "en": "TT-33 7.62x25 TT pistol"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "TT",
      "en": "TT"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "一把传奇的手枪。它经历过无数次的军事冲突，并经过一次又一次的改良，现在在世界上的很多地方仍可以见到它的踪影。这支手枪是TT-33最经典的量产版本，它类似勃朗宁手枪的枪管短后坐式自动原理，但其他方面不同，如结构更简单、单动扳机和采用击锤不到位的保险方式，使它能够经受住暴力的操作。由于大威力的7.62x25子弹和相对较长的枪管，TT具有高初速和高穿透力的特点，即使在较远的距离上也依旧保持着相当高的精准度。",
      "en": "A legendary pistol that has seen numerous military conflicts throughout the years and is still in service in certain regions of the world, in one variation or another. This one is a classic TT-33, the most mass-produced version. It features a Browning short-recoil tilting-barrel system, but other than that, the construction design is very unique - it is purposefully simple, single-action, and no safety measures except half-cock notch, which makes it be able to withstand horrible operating abuse. Thanks to the powerful 7.62x25 cartridge and relatively long barrel, the TT boasts high muzzle velocity, penetration, and impressive accuracy, even over long distances."
    },
    "weight": 0.866,
